===Etymology===
Late {{etyl|enm|en}}, from {{etyl|frm|en}} {{term|vocatif|lang=frm}}, from {{etyl|la|en}} {{term|vocativus||calling|lang=la}}, from {{term|vocatus||invocation|lang=la}}, from {{term|vocare||to call|lang=la}}, from {{etyl|ine-pro|en}} {{m|ine-pro|*wek-}}, {{m|ine-pro|*wekʷ-}}, {{m|ine-pro|*wokʷ-||give vocal utterance, speak}}. See Latin {{term|vōx|lang=la}}.

